      <title>卢拉希望巴西航空公司救助计划附加条件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/lula-wants-strings-attached-to-brazil-s-rescue-plan-for-airlines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，巴西政府已向该国三大航空公司提交了针对航空业的援助计划，预计将在今年下半年公布结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/lula-wants-strings-attached-to-brazil-s-rescue-plan-for-airlines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
