      <title>保守党未能在英国早期竞选活动中削弱工党的民意调查领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/tories-fail-to-dent-labour-polling-lead-in-early-uk-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的工党仍领先里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党 22 个百分点，两位领导人正准备于周二进行电视辩论——这是英国大选活动以来的首场辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/tories-fail-to-dent-labour-polling-lead-in-early-uk-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
